siduction-btrfs (0.3.0-1) unstable; urgency=medium

  [Axel Konrad]
  * Rewritten with the aim of using the Snapper plugin directory.
  * GRUB is now able to extend the paths of kernel and initrd by the subvolumes.
  * So the systemd timer unit and the file 09_siduction-btrfs could be removed.
  * Support added for a boot partition when using GRUB.

 -- Torsten Wohlfarth <towo@siduction.org>  Sat, 02 Nov 2024 12:26:12 +0100

